：建立抗爭者唔係亂黎既形象，我地要成功我地所謂既革命，就要比市民知道佢地有我地既支持，拎到民意、為革命行出多一步又簡單易做。發表宣言後，仲可以令到元朗黑勢力有退落黎既空間（之後點處理佢地，我地贏左再算）"},{"pid":"38381208afaf189ebbbe95a8b6e10d91dabe8d4b","tid":1357664,"uid":267791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:59:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">兄弟爬山！！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"479fcf524c6eb00c05ac023b3fdac3f8fd2ca9d2","tid":1357664,"uid":176731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T19:02:54.000Z","msg":"727無黑勢力搞事既機率好低，但如果真係變到和理非，亦都符合以往我地既做法，亦解決到偏向中環既兄弟擔心既事（義士流失），之後既日子出其他地方抗爭，再有黑勢力出黎搞事，我地絕對唔會容忍"},{"pid":"d4008c48bc47b33b7bb649ccfd063f062c4a9494","tid":1357664,"uid":176731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38381208afaf189ebbbe95a8b6e10d91dabe8d4b","tid":1357664,"uid":267791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:59:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">兄弟爬山！！！！</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T19:04:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">各自努力</span></span>"},{"pid":"33e57cc5cf1896c137ac7612b14aa52ac6c4c3c5","tid":1357664,"uid":176731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T22:30:02.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"acb223dbf91b82776d6a5f8549034a728209b820","tid":1357664,"uid":176731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T22:30:20.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"fef27f0be56275244f682f78a59ffbdb795ef1cd","tid":1357664,"uid":176731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T22:30:35.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"}]}